{"tid":2298473,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"窮L改車音響，國王的新衣","createTime":"2020-11-24T05:32:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-26T01:40:39.000Z","uid":385014,"like":24,"dislike":59,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ad3825aae237fd28f877d2aae8e8d9853da59c","tid":2298473,"uid":385014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-24T05:32:05.000Z","msg":"問過幾間車音響，換全車喇叭都要HK$6,000 &ndash; HK$7,000。<br />\r前排work from home，又無錢，所以自己改車音響。<br />\r因為除左自我感覺良好外，沒什麼特別，這是我的國王的新衣。<br />\r<br />\r玩音響，鑽牛角尖已成風氣。<br />\r大抵，出花樣的人可以不求甚解，總之語不驚人誓不休，講得出就算數，講得多就是權威。<br />\r但亦有將電子、音響學理論發展附會者，此一派最難攪，因為他們都似乎懂多少理論，弊在將理論錯誤運用。<br />\rHi Fi 可以無師自通，之所以趨之若鶩也。最過癮者輒為：閣下若聽不出分別，是因為：1）機不夠班。2）聾。3）兩者兼具。此皇帝之新衣也。<br />\r\n<br />\n真空管前級放大消雜音<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9qAorM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9qAorM.png&h=5d155d78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/30cvckb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F30cvckb.png&h=c79e1102&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\n真空管信號顯示管<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hRqXBNC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhRqXBNC.png&h=a8ee941f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8pZQWNL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8pZQWNL.png&h=568eb84f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3WS97U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3WS97U.png&h=9313aa16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n控制電線則用上單股實心銅線，能塑造出不同形狀的走線，為電線路添上特別的藝術色彩！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JWLHN0s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJWLHN0s.png&h=1a2bc3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qNfkzFw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqNfkzFw.png&h=46c45c2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ahcSqNf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FahcSqNf.png&h=cace4178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qac7eFF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQac7eFF.png&h=6a6b0b42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DOnCBT4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDOnCBT4.png&h=d074da2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r日光之下出現了新事<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cA6cqOf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcA6cqOf.png&h=8482b68b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Emym3z0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEmym3z0.png&h=e5c1dc2d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6aKhBU6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6aKhBU6.png&h=e29c5dc2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1DmG3Ab.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1DmG3Ab.png&h=f2a30a0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YivXBVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYivXBVh.png&h=b91b14b7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RGEdUG2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRGEdUG2.png&h=4453769d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/06kpgVs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F06kpgVs.png&h=9327e1f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\rJVC 300W二手音箱 （有一日行過垃圾房見到）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TB8eEan.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTB8eEan.png&h=0e194daa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uoiimoO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuoiimoO.png&h=a6708155&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n\r8支金封管提供無損動力，左右聲道各由4支金封管獨立提供無損音<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tzGDmrb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtzGDmrb.png&h=11a36d7d&s={SIZE}